on this slide, which is, number one,

00:33:51.650 --> 00:33:57.240
to accelerate progress in cancer
including prevention and screening

00:33:57.240 --> 00:34:02.140
and expanding the gamut of research
from basic research all the way

00:34:02.140 --> 00:34:05.350
up through standard of care.

00:34:05.350 --> 00:34:08.720
