can subvert the body--

01:07:09.320 --> 01:07:13.560
body's response by elaborating
chemicals that might block signals.

01:07:13.560 --> 01:07:16.960
And you can actually attack
that with drugs and antibodies.

01:07:16.960 --> 01:07:21.170
