can attack the heart

01:20:25.070 --> 01:20:28.450 position:56%
in ways we never even dreamt before.

01:20:28.450 --> 01:20:33.340 position:56%
And we all have to become sensitized
and, you know, sharpen our readings

01:20:33.340 --> 01:20:35.230
so that we can understand
what has to be done,

01:20:35.230 --> 01:20:37.770
and sharing that information
so that we can all learn

01:20:37.770 --> 01:20:40.070
